Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.smartmodel

Class SmartModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.model.smartmodel.SmartModel
  • public class SmartModel
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all the useful information of the model that must be available to the player. This class can be easily serialized and de-serialized, which is a very important feature for an object that must surf the network.
